{"tid":2268860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：中港通關係社會訴求","createTime":"2020-11-03T06:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T06:29:55.000Z","uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bef63cb6534f2f890ff1ac2c4271232c48f1063d","tid":2268860,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:14:54.000Z","msg":"林鄭表示，今日下午開始的訪京之旅，除了會跟中央官員爭取提振經濟的措施外，亦會爭取免檢疫通關，「雖然我哋提出好多經濟政策，關於航空、金融範疇都係好重要，但現時對普羅大眾最重要都係『通關』，可以恢復兩地人員往來，不受 14 日加 14 日的檢疫限制。」林鄭說，明白疫情期間市民不能來回兩地探親，商界亦對檢疫令感到困擾，因此今次食物及衞生局局長陳肇始都會一同上京，講解本港疫情防控工作，希望成功爭取「通關」。"},{"pid":"2d099c87128c7ea6b75159d996d58fb64b81b3a1","tid":2268860,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:15:36.000Z","msg":"咁五大呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd79a4b0574b1f5a96704db3162208a39839190","tid":2268860,"uid":221343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:16:55.000Z","msg":"乜Q都話市民訴求社會訴求,食屎啦賤婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc95dd8af08e51f8575058edead18c7b8b876489","tid":2268860,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:19:19.000Z","msg":"留係大灣區算啦，唔好再黎香港"},{"pid":"de6f5bcbf14fa148bb1417ed20bb12203b7528a0","tid":2268860,"uid":268591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:22:46.000Z","msg":"又做戲<br />\n通到唔使搞咁多野啦<br />\n又呃班藍屍"},{"pid":"8d45f8caf4dad87d38d118f7b84f858cc0fe9f7b","tid":2268860,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfd79a4b0574b1f5a96704db3162208a39839190","tid":2268860,"uid":221343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:16:55.000Z","msg":"乜Q都話市民訴求社會訴求,食屎啦賤婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:23:35.000Z","msg":"五大訴求？"},{"pid":"18f9a84